      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just that the weight of it all is so heavy. it feels less like a chapter and more like the train has reached the end of the line and the tracks just... stop. there's a certain peace in realizing you don't have to keep traveling anymore. i keep thinking about how much easier it would be to just stop moving, to just let the journey end here. it feels like the only logical place to exit.",
